text: “hrux phwk cea khid wa phwk cea ca thuk plxy wi doy thi xallxh yang midi thrng ru brrda phu thi txsu nı hmu phwk cea læa midi yudthux pheuxn snith xun ca kxallxh læa rx sul khxng phraxngkh læa xun cak phu sraththa thanghlay læa xallxh nan thrng rxbru xyang laxeiyd nı sing thi phwk cea kratha”
